title: #61* Babies Having Babies (Patrick Coppolino)
itunes:title: Babies Having Babies with Patrick Coppolino - Part 1
description: Patrick Coppolino came to my hotel room in Toronto to talk about being a 21 year old out of work father. I tried my best to make him and that girl get an abortion but nothing worked. Let this be an inspiration or a clear warning to everyone who wants a baby. This is all in the realm of possibility.
